### Frontend — SSE Dashboard

#### [MODIFY] [Dashboard.jsx](file:///Users/mac/Desktop/CHAINVOTE/frontend/src/pages/Dashboard.jsx)
Complete rewrite from REST polling to SSE:
- On mount: read `repo` from `sessionStorage`
- Open `POST /api/v1/github/sync` then pipe to `ReadableStream` (fetch-based SSE, since GitHub POST requires body)
- Parse `data: {...}` lines as they arrive
- `type: "status"` → update status pill
- `type: "cluster_found"` → append cluster card with staggered mount animation
- `type: "complete"` → show completion state
- State: `streaming: bool`, `clusters: []`, `statusMsg: string`
- Remove `@tanstack/react-query` dependency from this page

---

